Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.48,0:00:53.44,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}問いかけたまま
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.74,0:00:59.62,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}答えはもう届かなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.58,0:01:07.83,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}溢れた感情を失くさないで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.88,0:01:13.88,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}心があれば守り抜けるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.88,0:01:19.97,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}命の音が聞こえるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:25.98,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}心の中 きみがいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.98,0:01:28.27,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}We will remember your name
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.27,0:01:30.57,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}We will remember your dream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.57,0:01:32.19,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}Remember you're braver
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.19,0:01:34.36,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}We will remember your name
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.36,0:01:36.70,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}We will remember your dream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.70,0:01:38.82,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}Remember you're braver
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.11,0:01:44.25,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}朱く焼けた世界を闇が青に染めて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.25,0:01:46.25,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}この目で見た
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.25,0:01:48.63,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}その目に焼き付いた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.79,0:01:50.96,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}Remember you're braver
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.13,0:01:53.76,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}遥かなる道を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.05,0:01:57.22,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}積み重なる悲しみを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.38,0:02:01.18,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}きみと生きよう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.22,0:02:06.02,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}僅かな望みを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.27,0:02:09.27,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}答えのないその問いを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.27,0:02:10.90,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}もう一度
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.02,0:02:14.90,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}もう二度と
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.48,0:00:53.44,OPCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}叩問內心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.74,0:00:59.62,OPCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}終究沒有得到答案
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.58,0:01:07.83,OPCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}不要忘記曾經滿腔的熱忱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.88,0:01:13.88,OPCNcht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}只要本心尚存便能守護至終
